Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:03.65,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}音も無く迫る闇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:09.05,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}光を灯す為 今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:11.37,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}ぶち壊すFate & Fear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:14.98,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生まれ持った衝動で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:21.37,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}全てを掴み獲れ今すぐ ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:25.11,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}真実を手に!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:53.16,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}扣下击断烦恼的扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:57.56,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毫无用处的自尊在垃圾回收日舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:02.56,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}猎取一切的武士疯狂起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:06.29,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}内燃机频频轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:08.65,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍将延续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:12.81,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使是糜烂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:17.51,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在叹息之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:21.39,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}跟随神风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.93,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}向着未知之处前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:28.93,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鼎沸的热情与
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:34.13,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}熏染的灵魂勒紧胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:38.59,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}如同燃烧的火焰般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:41.11,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能在此找到自己的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:44.50,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}雷达之下寻找自己的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:50.96,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起钢刃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:59.53,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}纵情呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:06.74,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}继续这不羁的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:18.60,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃焦这唯一的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:23.80,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}前进直到血干枯之时
